df1["Date"]=df1["Date"].astype("datetime64[ns]")
#df1.info()

df1["Year"]=pd.DatetimeIndex(df1["Date"]).year
#df1.head()

df1["Month"]=pd.DatetimeIndex(df1["Date"]).month

df1["PVSyst_Egrid_MTD"]=df1.groupby(by=["Block","Year","Month"])["PVSyst_EGrid"].cumsum()

df1["PVSyst_PR"]=(df1["PVSyst_EGrid"]/df1["DC_Capacity"])/df1["PVSyst_GII"]

df1["Ins.Delta"]=(df1["GII"]-df1["PVSyst_GII"])/df1["PVSyst_GII"]

df1["YesterdayImportEnergyMeter"]=df1.sort_values(by=['Block','Date'],ascending=True).groupby(by=["Block"])["ImportEnergyMeter"].shift(1)
df1["ImportEnergy"]=df1["ImportEnergyMeter"]-df1["YesterdayImportEnergyMeter"]
#df1.sort_values(by=['Block','Date'],ascending=True)


df1["NetEnergy"]=df1["ExportEnergy"]-df1["ImportEnergy"]

df1["AC_Loss"]=(df1["InvEnergy"]-df1["NetEnergy"])/df1["InvEnergy"]

df1["NetEnergy_MTD"]=df1.groupby(by=["Block","Year","Month"])["NetEnergy"].cumsum()

df1["ExpectedEnergy"]=(df1["DC_Capacity"]*df1["GII"]*df1["PVSyst_PR"]*df1["GA"])/100

df1["EPI"]=df1["NetEnergy"]/df1["ExpectedEnergy"]

df1["SPPr"]=(df1["NetEnergy"]/df1["PVSyst_EGrid"])*100

df1["PR"]=(((df1["NetEnergy"]/df1["DC_Capacity"])/df1["GII"])/df1["GA"])*10000

df1["CUF_DC"]=(((df1["NetEnergy"]/df1["DC_Capacity"])/24))*100

df1["CUF_AC"]=(df1["NetEnergy"]/50/24)*100

df1["Rvnu"]=df1["NetEnergy"]*2.73/1000

df1["Rvnu_MTD"]=df1.groupby(by=["Block","Year","Month"])["Rvnu"].cumsum()
